= Personalization =

  * config/blog.yaml contains the Asterisell parameters;
  * config/html.erb contains:
    * code generating Java Analytics Scripts;
    * code generating header;
    * code generating footer;
    * code generating menu and all left sidebar content;
  * input/styles/common contains:
    * #header tag;
    * #personalization of footer with text-size: small;
    
